        "content": "Untested and cheap to cover — also would have caught the `radiomadagasikara-rnm` mismatch noted above.\n\n```python\nfrom providers import PROVIDERS\n\nclass TestProvidersRegistry:\n    def test_all_entries_are_newssource_subclasses(self):\n        from base import NewsSource\n        for cls in PROVIDERS.values():\n            assert issubclass(cls, NewsSource)\n\n    def test_key_matches_source_name(self):\n        for key, cls in PROVIDERS.items():\n            assert cls.source_name == key\n\n    def test_every_provider_can_list_or_has_sitemap(self):\n        # every provider either sets sitemap_url or overrides list_article_urls\n        for cls in PROVIDERS.values():\n            has_sitemap = cls.sitemap_url is not None\n            overrides = cls.list_article_urls is not __import__(\"base\").NewsSource.list_article_urls\n            assert has_sitemap or overrides, f\"{cls.source_name} has neither\"\n```\n\n---\n\n",
